%% Diagram: Writable.write / drain backpressure handshake
%% Type: sequence
sequenceDiagram
  participant P as Producer
  participant W as Writable
  participant C as Consumer

  loop While buffer below highWaterMark
    P->>W: write(chunk)
    W-->>P: true
    W->>C: flush
  end

  P->>W: write(chunk)
  W-->>P: false (buffer reached highWaterMark)
  Note over P: Pause production.<br/>Subscribe once('drain', resume)
  W->>C: flush remaining
  C-->>W: ack
  W-->>P: 'drain' event
  Note over P: Resume writes.

  Note over P,W: Ignoring the false return<br/>buffers indefinitely → OOM.
